n<span style=\"color: red;\">Ps我今年中二，無法打工幫補家計</span><br />\nPs2其實係我誤信前死黨，自己on99衰多口，同左佢講。結果佢一聽到，就即刻大叫「吓你啊媽係雞？」先會搞成日。對唔住係我天真我誤信人，放心已絕交☺，我已經冇哂朋友。不過我都唔需要呢啲人做我朋友，會拉低智商😂</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"></span><br />\n<br />\n2016-12-5"},{"pid":"8daa514cbbdaae93f80deb00b4b29cfc94615067","tid":310323,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T23:55:23.000Z","msg":"30幾歲已經係中年大叔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecb5d0c1152eae04f423d02f9d7a119d70d37bd7","tid":310323,"uid":126652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T00:06:52.000Z","msg":"我當你講既野係真 點解被中出咁多次都冇大肚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40cd0f8c13929e9b9e764e59bc0b47695378a0d8","tid":310323,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T00:19:50.000Z","msg":"肛交要21歲"},{"pid":"58e835fed8a5ed143891e6b6c25a7f755408595f","tid":310323,"uid":5928,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T00:20:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>16年12月你先話自己中二，7個月後變中四。好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樓豬好似係quote fb post喎清"},{"pid":"ff4f78a07c5af83ca62a17dcae55705e906c4190","tid":310323,"uid":29804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T00:23:36.000Z","msg":"男女性交 16歲<br />\n男男肛交 16歲<br />\n男女肛交 21歲"},{"pid":"fbf567e4a27209d2c9db831a0f1d25a1a9782083","tid":310323,"uid":14197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T01:19:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>16年12月你先話自己中二，7個月後變中四。好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇d唔睇d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21461f46e75bb742c09bd64cd4915624a1abaef8","tid":310323,"uid":14197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-0